/PG804/XX/PR
May I ever learn to find my place among the people of Israel./PR
May my heart be a Jewish heart,/PR
my mind a Jewish mind,/PR
my soul a Jewish soul./PR
May all my actions bring a good name to the word Jew./PR
/PR
