Be kind and gentle./PR
May I find my home in the House of Prayer,/PR
My life in the tasks of my people,/PR
My words in the words spoken truly in the name of all that is/PR
good,/PR
My deeds a credit to my people./PR
/PR
May law rule over all the earth; and justice and mercy/PR
be everlasting./PR
May the Messianic days come soon and in my own life, bringing/PR
peace and hope to all./PR
And may I take my place beside those who love and serve all that/PR
