/PL805/XXMEDITATIONS FOR ELUL/XX/PR
/KAMEDITATIONS FOR ELUL/XX/PR
/PR
God, help me through the days of Elul to prepare myself for the
New Year with its promise of new life for my body and my soul./PR
Help me face questions I wish to avoid!/PR
Help me accept truths that do not comfort!/PR
I wish to journey to the light, but the path to it is hidden by
all the promises I never kept, by the goodness I deserted./PR
May the words from the past show me the way of return./PR
I begin the road of repentance. Meet me, God, as I journey
on it./PR
